These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, juice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, balloon-flower, aconite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, september, june
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who growsaconite##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage         | mirinda | 7up   | juice   |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | azalea | aconite |
| Birthday   | june  | august    | september      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

