.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, poker
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, lilac, pink
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person eating kale is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who likes ivory is between the person playing scrabble and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Game   | scrabble     | poker     | snooker      |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Color           | pink | ivory     | lilac       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, brown, lavender
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, october
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, lacrosse
1. the bartender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the paramedic and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Color          | pink  | lavender     | brown     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| Birthday   | january  | march    | october |
| Sport           | lacrosse     | soccer | climbing |

