.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, documentary, animation
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, fishing
City: berlin, miami, hamburg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person traveling to berlin##2
4. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | musical       | animation  | documentary   |
| Hobby     | puzzles    | fishing  | hiking |
| City     | miami   | hamburg | berlin        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

