.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
City: hamburg, marseilles, rome
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, almond-milk
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, chess
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City          | rome    | hamburg     | marseilles      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | sprite       | cola       |
| Game           | bridge     | mah-jongg       | chess     |

