.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, paramedic, doctor
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, tennis, volleyball
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose, tulip
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the doctor is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the paramedic and the person who growsrose##2
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
5. the software-developer is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Job          | paramedic | software-developer | doctor    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Sport   | skiing   | tennis     | volleyball        |
| Flower           | daisy      | tulip       | rose      |

