.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, firefighter, software-developer
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, polish, american
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, water, mirinda
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the polish is between the software-developer and the person driving the car##2
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the polish is between the american and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Job          | software-developer      | firefighter   | entrepreneur |
| Nationality         | indonesian | polish | american |
| Beverage   | milk      | mirinda | water   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

