.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, turkish-climbing
3 different games are played: backgammon, poker, snooker
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, spanish, turkish
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the spanish##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person drinking water##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | cola       | soy-milk      | water      |
| Sport         | water-polo    | turkish-climbing | volleyball      |
| Game           | snooker | backgammon     | poker |
| Nationality   | spanish     | turkish          | nigerian       |

