.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar, swisher
3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, lilac, yellow
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes yellow##2
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | pall-mall      | bolivar | swisher     |
| Game          | scrabble   | billiard      | chess     |
| Color   | yellow  | coral      | lilac |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi        | bike     |

