The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, action
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, daffodil
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person eating asparagus##2
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who growslily is the person watching action movies##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
