.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat, bird
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
House: tower, art-deco, craftsman
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, swimming
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Pet      | bird     | cat | guinea-pig      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| House   | craftsman   | art-deco         | tower     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | snowboarding    | swimming     |

