.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, lilac, coral
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, boat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, rugby
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who likes coral##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who likes lilac and the person driving the bike##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Color           | azure | coral | lilac |
| Transport   | bike     | boat        | quad-bike         |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | parkour    | rugby        |

