There 3 different types of food: lime, corn, plum
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who growstulip is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person playing whist##2
4. the person eating corn is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Flower           | lily | tulip        | daffodil       |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | time-travel |
| Game           | whist     | mah-jongg         | chess  |
