.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, spanish, american
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, orange, red
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
House: townhouse, wooden, modern
1. the american is between the wooden house and the person who likes red##2
2. the american is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the spanish##1
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the person who likes lavender is the wooden house##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Nationality      | spanish    | american          | italian |
| Color          | red | orange           | lavender        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| House   | townhouse    | modern    | wooden      |

