3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person who growspoppy is between the art-deco house and the person who growsdaffodil##2
5. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Flower          | iris  | poppy   | daffodil |
