.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, february
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, golf, parkour
There 3 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, papaya
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person eating carrot and the person who's birthday is in august##2
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating carrot##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Flower       | balloon-flower | orchid | amaryllis |
| Birthday         | august   | february       | december        |
| Sport       | parkour | cricket   | golf         |
| Food   | papaya    | kiwi     | carrot         |

