.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, pall-mall, dannemann
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, cherry, plum
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, sprite
1. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person drinking sprite and the siglo-smoker##2
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person eating plum is the fan of disco##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cherry##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Cigar   | dannemann    | pall-mall | siglo |
| Food           | lettuce        | plum   | cherry  |
| Beverage     | sprite      | coffee   | almond-milk |

