.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, blend
City: rome, london, nizza
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, apricot, yellow
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
6. the blend-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the person who likes apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar           | oliveros   | blend   | havana |
| City   | nizza | london   | rome     |
| Color   | apricot     | lilac      | yellow    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

