.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, sailing, handball
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, russian, canadian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
City: edinburgh, colone, liverpool
1. the person traveling to colone is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person who's sport is tennis and the spanish##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | tennis | handball     | sailing        |
| Nationality         | russian   | canadian | spanish |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| City           | liverpool           | edinburgh    | colone       |

