.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, cain, oliveros
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, board-games, traveling
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, scientific, comedy
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person driving the car##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the car##1
4. the person watching romance movies is the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person driving the tram and the person watching scientific movies##2
6. the person watching comedy movies is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar        | cain      | davidoff | oliveros |
| Hobby         | board-games     | traveling    | chess        |
| Movie-Genre       | scientific | comedy   | romance   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 